text: Ian Joseph Gorst (born 15 December 1969) is a Jersey politician. He is a member of the States Assembly since 5 December 2005 and is the Minister for External Relations. He was the Chief Minister of Jersey for two terms, from 18 November 2011 until 7 June 2018. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Chief Ministers of Jersey Category:Politicians from Lancashire
